(101, 1, '2011-11-22 07:37:05', '2011-11-22 07:37:05', '<!--:vi--><div id="divNoiDungChinh">\r\n\r\n<strong>Lĩnh vực hoạt động</strong>\r\n\r\no          Xây dựng website thương mại điện tử, website giới thiệu cho doanh nghiệp, tổ chức.\r\n\r\no          Xây dựng cổng thông tin, ứng dụng công công nghệ thông tin trong giáo dục.\r\n\r\no          Triển khai hệ thống quản lý và phát triển phần mềm giải pháp cho doanh nghiệp.\r\n\r\no          Gia công và xuất khẩu phần mềm theo tiêu chuẩn quốc tế cho thị trường ngoài nước.\r\n\r\no          Xây dựng website tin tức.\r\n\r\nTầm nhìn\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div><!--:--><!--:en--><h3>We have been helping clients with high-quality web &amp;amp; graphics Designs that suit their products &amp;amp; services. Providing complete Internet solutions as well as corporate identity, we offer you effective design solutions at most economical rates.</h3>\r\nWe provide web sites designs, software gui and development solutions at a affordable rate for every one. Our affordable freelance web site design solutions will shape up your online presence in a distinctive manner in your expertise field and we will give a look and feel to step ahead from competitors.\r\n\r\nAs a freelance web designer, we provide a range of web services - from a standard web designing to complex solutions, such as Logo Design, Graphic Design, Flash Animation, Software GUI, Listing in Search engines etc - above all providing the client with an affordable but effective solution is our aim. We are also doing redesign and update existing web pages work, produce a web site from a web template you may have, or redesign an existing web site. Our main aim is to provide the most complete Internet business solutions available at cheap cost and done by professional freelance web designer.<!--:-->', '<!--:vi-->Giới thiệu<!--:--><!--:en-->About<!--:-->', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-10', '', '', '2011-11-22 07:37:05', '2011-11-22 07:37:05', '', 6, 'http://ta