act-forms/lonroth-oldesign-inspiring-creative-contact-form.jpg" alt="lonroth-oldesign-inspiring-creative-contact-form" width="570" height="291" /></a>\r\n<h2>74. <a href="http://www.august.com.au/contact-us/" target="_blank">Contact August Creative Agency</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.august.com.au/contact-us/" target="_blank"><img src="http://cdn1.1stwebdesigner.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/modern-web-contact-forms/august-inspiring-creative-contact-form.jpg" alt="august-inspiring-creative-contact-form" width="570" height="280" /></a>\r\n<h2>75.<a href="http://www.helenguttridge.com/contact.htm" target="_blank"> Contact Helen Guttridge</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.helenguttridge.com/contact.htm" target="_blank"><img src="http://cdn1.1stwebdesigner.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/modern-web-contact-forms/helen-guttridge-inspiring-creative-contact-form.jpg" alt="helen-guttridge-inspiring-creative-contact-form" width="570" height="435" /></a>\r\n<h2>Extremely Original and Creative Contact Form Solutions (15 Examples)</h2>\r\n<h2>76.<a href="http://weloveicons.com/contact/" target="_blank">Contact We Love Icons</a></h2>\r\nEven if you don’t have anything to say, this contact form invites to fill empty fields!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://weloveicons.com/contact/" target="_blank"><img src="http://cdn1.1stwebdesigner.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/modern-web-contact-forms/we-love-icons-inspiring-creative-contact-form.jpg" alt="we-love-icons-inspiring-creative-contact-form" width="570" height="569" /></a>\r\n<h2>77. <a href="http://www.gpacheco.fr/#contact" target="_blank">Contact Guillaume Pacheco</a></h2>\r\n<a href="http://www.gpacheco.fr/#contact" target="_blank"><img src="http://cdn1.1stwebdesigner.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/modern-web-contact-forms/gpachecho-inspiring-creative-contact-form.jpg" alt="gpachecho-inspiring-creative-contact-form" width="570" height="272" /></a>\r\n<h2>78.<a href="http://yodaa.com/#contact" target="_blank"> Contact Yodaa</a></h2>\r\n<h